              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>rest</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to rest</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In the use of ἀναπαύομαι[a] and ἀνάπαυσις[b], the focus of meaning seems to be upon the restorative character of rest rather than mere cessation of activity (see {D:68.34}).</Comments>
